the both of you.

14:43.550 --> 14:47.955
And I know Marty would really
be happy if you came.

14:49.056 --> 14:52.492
I appreciate that,
but I just can't.

14:53.393 --> 14:54.761
It would be too hard on me.

14:54.861 --> 14:57.197
Yeah. Yeah, I-I
could see that.

14:57.297 --> 14:58.999
I had to try though, huh?

14:59.099 --> 15:00.767
All right.

15:00.968 --> 15:02.970
Get back to it.

15:04.271 --> 15:05.405
You know...

15:05.505 --> 15:09.242
Necie, I just wanted
you to know that...

15:10.143 --> 15:13.746
...that Marty's not gonna be
the only one that'll miss you.

15:13.846 --> 15:15.648
We all will.

15:15.748 --> 15:17.985
You were
part of our family, and...

15:17.985 --> 15:21.221
we never got a chance
to say a real goodbye.

15:27.127 --> 15:28.895
I'm gonna miss you guys, too.

15:30.330 --> 15:31.631
Uh...

15:31.731 --> 15:33.366
I'd give you a hug,
but I'm really sweaty.

15:33.466 --> 15:35.435
Oh, it's all good.

15:35.535 --> 15:37.070
I jogged in from
the parking lot,

15:37.170 --> 15:38.671
