15:43.410 --> 15:45.178
Okay. Yeah, go.

15:45.278 --> 15:47.714
Go.
Get-get back to it.

15:55.122 --> 15:56.523
Oh! Napkin! Napkin!

15:56.623 --> 15:58.191
Napkin!
Okay.

15:58.291 --> 15:59.559
Ladies and gentlemen,

15:59.659 --> 16:00.760
