17:41.528 --> 17:43.730
I was raised to be hard

17:43.830 --> 17:46.499
and never express
my feelings.

17:46.599 --> 17:50.270
But sometimes being
Butler strong means

17:50.370 --> 17:54.040
being strong enough to
admit when you're hurting.

17:55.308 --> 17:58.044
Did I not tell you that part?

17:58.145 --> 17:59.579
No.

17:59.679 --> 18:02.349
