said the opposite.

18:02.449 --> 18:05.185
Yeah... Look,

18:05.285 --> 18:06.953
I'm sorry if I made you feel

18:07.053 --> 18:09.222
like you had to
be tough, for me.

18:10.823 --> 18:12.925
