18:23.170 --> 18:25.338
Hi.

18:26.306 --> 18:27.840
What are you doing here?

18:27.940 --> 18:30.943
Your dad told me the vegan pigs
in a blanket were delicious.

18:33.045 --> 18:36.048
Yeah, yeah,
everybody loved them.

18:37.617 --> 18:39.186
You want some?

18:40.420 --> 18:41.754
Uh, there's a lot left.

18:41.854 --> 18:43.190
No-no, thanks.

18:47.694 --> 18:48.995
How you doing?

18:49.095 --> 18:51.264
I'm okay.

18:52.865 --> 18:55.868
Considering today
was supposed to be...

18:57.670 --> 18:59.306
You know?

18:59.406 --> 19:02.642
Yeah, I know.

19:02.742 --> 19:04.444
It's too bad.

19:04.544 --> 19:09.081
