what is this?

20:18.818 --> 20:21.187
Is that the ring?

20:21.288 --> 20:23.556
Yeah, it is.

20:23.656 --> 20:26.626
Necie must've stuck this in
my pocket while we were dancing.

20:26.726 --> 20:29.161
Well, all right.

20:30.397 --> 20:31.598
What?

20:31.698 --> 20:34.801
The boy don't need to be
brokenhearted and broke.

20:36.803 --> 20:40.507
Mrs. Butler, I must say,

20:40.607 --> 20:43.876
once again, you look
great in this dress.

20:43.976 --> 20:45.945
Well, enjoy it, because this

20:46.045 --> 20:48.315
is the last time
you're gonna see it.

20:52.919 --> 20:55.455
Please tell me that
was your spine.

